{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887166070,"sessionID":"ses_284e07bf1ffeI2NbuA7BTcCAfj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b1fa1ef001jWJmiCiD4QCob0","messageID":"msg_d7b1f94d8001M7Sc0Kia6YuOTU","sessionID":"ses_284e07bf1ffeI2NbuA7BTcCAfj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_6b1cdb7d990e4ba89b37d279","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Docusaurus documentation site framework for the agentcube project.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-042\n10: - **Module**: `docs`\n11: - **Language**: TypeScript\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Spec**: TBD\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Scenario: Project Initialization\n18: \n19: ### AR-042-001: Initialize Docusaurus project\n20: \n21: - **GIVEN** a new docs module requirement\n22: - **WHEN** initializing a Docusaurus project\n23: - **THEN** it SHALL use TypeScript for type safety\n24: - **AND** SHALL follow the standard Docusaurus project structure\n25: \n26: ### AR-042-002: Dependency configuration\n27: \n28: - **GIVEN** package.json configuration\n29: - **WHEN** setting up dependencies\n30: - **THEN** it SHALL include docusaurus package\n31: - **AND** SHALL include necessary TypeScript types\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## Scenario: Documentation Structure\n36: \n37: ### AR-042-003: Documentation directory structure\n38: \n39: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus project\n40: - **WHEN** organizing documentation\n41: - **THEN** it SHALL have proper docs directory layout\n42: - **AND** SHALL include sidebar configuration\n43: \n44: ### AR-042-004: Custom components\n45: \n46: - **GIVEN** documentation site\n47: - **WHEN** extending Docusaurus\n48: - **THEN** it SHALL support custom React components\n49: - **AND** SHALL include proper TypeScript typing\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## Scenario: Build and Deployment\n54: \n55: ### AR-042-005: Build configuration\n56: \n57: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus project\n58: - **WHEN** configuring build process\n59: - **THEN** it SHALL produce optimized static files\n60: - **AND** SHALL support multiple output formats\n61: \n62: ### AR-042-006: Version documentation\n63: \n64: - **GIVEN** documentation site\n65: - **WHEN** managing versions\n66: - **THEN** it SHALL support documentation versioning\n67: - **AND** SHALL maintain versioned docs properly\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## References\n72: \n73: - Docusaurus: https://docusaurus.io/\n74: - TypeScript: https://www.typescriptlang.org/\n\n(End of file - total 74 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Docusaurus documentation site framework for the agentcube project.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-042\n- **Module**: `docs`\n- **Language**: TypeScript\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Spec**: TBD\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Project Initialization\n\n### AR-042-001: Initialize Docusaurus project\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775887166041,"end":1775887166067}}}}
