{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887208246,"sessionID":"ses_284e07bf1ffeI2NbuA7BTcCAfj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b201c6c001T8LzWCyiuYL806","messageID":"msg_d7b201168001jrUnesk87roW5U","sessionID":"ses_284e07bf1ffeI2NbuA7BTcCAfj","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_8de8aa7bfffa40fbaf7dc59b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-043 — Architecture Design Documents & API Documentation\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing architecture design documents and API documentation for the agentcube project.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-043\n- **Module**: `docs`\n- **Language**: Markdown\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Spec**: None (standalone requirement)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Architecture Design Document\n\n### AR-043-001: System architecture overview\n\n- **GIVEN** a new architecture design requirement\n- **WHEN** creating the system architecture document\n- **THEN** it SHALL include a high-level system diagram\n- **AND** SHALL document the core components (Agent Runtime, Code Interpreter, Router, Workload Manager)\n\n### AR-043-002: Component documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** architecture design document\n- **WHEN** documenting each component\n- **THEN** it SHALL describe the component's purpose and responsibilities\n- **AND** SHALL include component interactions and data flows\n\n### AR-043-003: Infrastructure documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** architecture design document\n- **WHEN** documenting infrastructure\n- **THEN** it SHALL describe the Kubernetes deployment topology\n- **AND** SHALL document the Helm chart structure and configuration\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: API Documentation\n\n### AR-043-004: SDK client API documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** agentcube Python SDK\n- **WHEN** generating API documentation\n- **THEN** it SHALL document the ControlPlaneClient class\n- **AND** SHALL document all public methods with parameter types and return values\n\n### AR-043-005: REST API endpoints documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** Workload Manager REST API\n- **WHEN** documenting API endpoints\n- **THEN** it SHALL document the `/v1/code-interpreter` endpoint\n- **AND** SHALL include request/response schemas and HTTP methods\n\n### AR-043-006: CLI command documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** agentcube CLI tool\n- **WHEN** documenting CLI commands\n- **THEN** it SHALL document all available commands\n- **AND** SHALL include usage examples and argument descriptions\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Kubernetes Resources Documentation\n\n### AR-043-007: CRD documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** AgentCube custom resource definitions\n- **WHEN** documenting CRDs\n- **THEN** it SHALL document AgentRuntime CRD schema\n- **AND** SHALL document CodeInterpreter CRD schema\n\n### AR-043-008: Helm values documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** Helm chart for AgentCube\n- **WHEN** documenting Helm values\n- **THEN** it SHALL document all configurable values\n- **AND** SHALL include default values and descriptions\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Documentation Organization\n\n### AR-043-009: Documentation structure\n\n- **GIVEN** documentation project\n- **WHEN** organizing documentation\n- **THEN** it SHALL follow Docusaurus directory structure\n- **AND** SHALL have separate sections for guides, API reference, and architecture\n\n### AR-043-010: Documentation navigation\n\n- **GIVEN** documentation site\n- **WHEN** configuring navigation\n- **THEN** it SHALL have a clear sidebar with logical grouping\n- **AND** SHALL support versioned documentation\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- AgentCube GitHub: https://github.com/agentcube/agentcube\n- Docusaurus: https://docusaurus.io/\n- Python Docstring Style: https://sphinx-rtd-tutorial.readthedocs.io/en/latest/docstrings.html","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/__init__.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775887208236,"end":1775887208244}}}}
